text.tspan: Number of people employed in agriculture, 1801 to 2019
Number of people of working age who were engaged in any activity to produce goods or provide services for pay or
profit in the agriculture sector (agriculture, hunting, forestry and fishing).
Source: Our World in Data based on International Labor Organization (via the World Bank) and historical sources
